name: Jimmy Fallon
monologue: The Republican candidates held another debate in South Carolina, and it went on about half-hour longer than expected. Which isn't bad, considering Trump's campaign has gone on half a year longer than expected.

name: Jimmy Fallon
monologue: Today, the moderators apologized for keeping viewers awake so late. Then viewers said, "You didn't."

name: Jimmy Fallon
monologue: Donald Trump tried bringing up polls that showed him winning, and the crowd actually started to boo. Trump was like, "See, even ghosts love me."

name: Jimmy Fallon
monologue: Last week near the Texas/Mexico border, authorities say they found a shipment of over a ton of marijuana that was disguised to look like carrots. Which explains why Bugs Bunny is now like, "Sup, doc?"
